    "synopsis": "A prequel-novella told across centuries — Chaplain Daenyathos as a sergeant at the Second Siege of Terra, then his slow rise as the Soul Drinkers' philosopher-soldier and author of their Catechisms Martial, then his interment in a dreadnought and disappearance. Daenyathos has watched the Imperium long enough to despise it, and the Catechisms are not the guidance his chapter believed — they are the long-game seed of its undoing.",
